				<div itemprop="commentText" class='post entry-content '>
					<p>I've found some debugger options for PHP:</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href='http://xdebug.org/' class='bbc_url' title='External link' rel='external'>http://xdebug.org/</a></p>
<p><a href='http://www.php-debugger.com/dbg/' class='bbc_url' title='External link' rel='external'>http://www.php-debugger.com/dbg/</a></p>
<p><a href='http://phpdbg.com/' class='bbc_url' title='External link' rel='external'>http://phpdbg.com/</a></p>
<p><a href='http://dbug.ospinto.com/' class='bbc_url' title='External link' rel='external'>http://dbug.ospinto.com/</a></p>
<p><a href='http://www.firephp.org/' class='bbc_url' title='External link' rel='external'>http://www.firephp.org/</a></p>
<p><a href='http://pecl.php.net/package/apd' class='bbc_url' title='External link' rel='external'>http://pecl.php.net/package/apd</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>And probably there are more. Do you guys know any of these debuggers? Do you recommend one? What is the best PHP debugger?</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>ps: I'm trying to avoid IDEs at the momment, I would like to use a tool specifically made for debugging.</p>

					
