<p>It is. I use it on a daily basis with a few large Symfony2 based applications. It's a great tool.<br><br><a href='http://thorpesystems.com/blog/debugging-php-in-vim' class='bbc_url' title='External link' rel='external'>http://thorpesystems...ging-php-in-vim</a><br><br>
